data.description: Move-in Ready! New Roof in 2022, New HVAC in 2021. All appliances will stay with the home.  This meticulously maintained residence boasts a beautiful floor plan perfect for comfortable living and entertaining. The main level features a welcoming foyer, a cozy living room with a view to the patio, a updated kitchen with modern appliances and ample cabinet space, and a convenient powder room for guests. Upstairs, you'll find the primary suite with a private bathroom and spacious closet, along with an addition spacious bedroom.  Outside, enjoy a  fenced patio perfect for relaxing in a hammock.  With its convenient location, and desirable neighborhood, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and charm.   Located in Atlanta's perimeter where easy commute to Atlanta's top schools/universities (Mercer, Emory, GA Tech, GA State) and is very convenient to travel Downtown Atlanta, CDC, Midtown Atlanta, Airport. Easy access to public transportation, highways (I-85, I-285) shopping, restaurants and parks.
